12T15:14:24.000Z","msg":"佢鍾意幾時食就幾時食，喺邊食就喺邊食，完全唔會理我存在，我只可臉為咗保護自己而死開。"},{"pid":"4996291e04e2bd9435705766139bec2badcadd08","tid":979288,"uid":98961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T15:15:37.000Z","msg":"買多啲俾佢食咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaa9c43228b7d93e04daed4278ef9c075d304a5d","tid":979288,"uid":17641,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T15:15:59.000Z","msg":"你連支煙都不如<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22df1f62cb90d0be2b2c1c2333de96ec9c0b6703","tid":979288,"uid":37363,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T15:19:14.000Z","msg":"佢嘅愛得把口講，根本從來無愛過我，每一刻都傷害我。"},{"pid":"3293ebd2eb72f642fbb9ab61ba2b7e4a373ad864","tid":979288,"uid":52740,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T15:20:06.000Z","msg":"硬係覺得你呀媽後生時係d學壞左人生是是但但d MK妹黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  都唔似個正常家長"},{"pid":"8e4518e95458f080aa48a458d6a3e714e441315a","tid":979288,"uid":37363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aaa9c43228b7d93e04daed4278ef9c075d304a5d","tid":979288,"uid":17641,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T15:15:59.000Z","msg":"你連支煙都不如<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T15:20:44.000Z","msg":"我都覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢會寧願我搬走都唔食少一支煙，想我快啲死開唔好煩住佢。"},{"pid":"a9d71502c6256c3b71e0ca43c9202f5044689916","tid":979288,"uid":37363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3293ebd2eb72f642fbb9ab61ba2b7e4a373ad864","tid":979288,"uid":52740,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T15:20:06.000Z","msg":"硬係覺得你呀媽後生時係d學壞左人生是是但但d MK妹黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  都唔似個正常家長"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T15:25:02.000Z","msg":"無從考究<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 淨係覺得佢性格好差"},{"pid":"cf43c0bb42fa94e28176db26ab2db77d0a8fbcc0","tid":979288,"uid":37363,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T15:27:24.000Z","msg":"唔只食煙唔理人感受，玩唱K app都係，朝朝10點幾唱到大大聲，又要成屋人唔出聲就佢，我要出門會畀佢催住，要我快啲畀晒間屋佢用。重要唔知自己幾撚嘈，夜晚食飯讚返自己唱得高分。<br />\n<br />\n呢啲性格嘅人唔死都無用，無資格有我呢個女。"},{"pid":"b276e8c4c69d50934dfde6cf0d8290efac72ad14","tid":979288,"uid":11320,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T15:46:15.000Z","msg":"我老母好偉大<br />\n一食就關門係自己房再塞毛巾 密室咁自己食<br />\n搞到我好擔心佢 寧願佢開埋門通風 唔好咁傷身 <br />\n好在最近佢都無再點食了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有好老母先會有正面思想"},{"pid":"2e50295234882b68531c44906e612e469d97bda3","tid":979288,"uid":19501,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T15:57:08.000Z","msg":"叫佢食多啲鹹魚，加工肉類，飲多啲酒<br />\n都係第一類致癌物，對人體無害"},{"pid":"b6041c2789b083bfd9181b0aa4ec9593e548de4f","tid":979288,"uid":12696,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T16:07:23.000Z","msg":"你食埋一份啦<br />\nIf u can&rsquo;t beat them , join them"}]}